The "ItemAutoSubmit" plugin for the Echo Submit Form allows to post the content of the submit form to Echo StreamServer when the user presses the Enter key. It enables a chat-like behavior.

Version: 2.0 (04/29/2011)
Developed by: Echo Solutions team (Kushnir Andrew)
Documentation: http://wiki.aboutecho.com/Community-Developed-Plugins#ItemAutoSubmit
